<p><strong><big><big>Table of Contents:</big></big></strong></p>
<!-- START: Quick Index: 0eb18a5a91f07cbe33de8a273a05a9cc --><div class="rl_quickindex card"><div class="card-body"><ol class="index index-level-2"><li class="index-item"><a href="/03/index.php/en/divine-revelation-or-a-human-drama?format=feed&type=rss#following-jews-and-limiting-the-maximum-number-of-wives-to-4" data-heading="following-jews-and-limiting-the-maximum-number-of-wives-to-4" class="index-link">Following Jews and limiting the maximum number of wives to 4</a><li class="index-item"><a href="/03/index.php/en/divine-revelation-or-a-human-drama?format=feed&type=rss#the-1st-role-of-revelation-about-zaynab-bint-jahsh" data-heading="the-1st-role-of-revelation-about-zaynab-bint-jahsh" class="index-link">The 1st Role of Revelation about Zaynab bint Jahsh</a><li class="index-item"><a href="/03/index.php/en/divine-revelation-or-a-human-drama?format=feed&type=rss#the-2nd-role-of-revelation-when-muhammad-fell-in-love-with-zaynab" data-heading="the-2nd-role-of-revelation-when-muhammad-fell-in-love-with-zaynab" class="index-link">The 2nd Role of Revelation when Muhammad fell in love with Zaynab</a><li class="index-item"><a href="/03/index.php/en/divine-revelation-or-a-human-drama?format=feed&type=rss#the-3rd-role-of-revelation-verse-33-38-declares-that-allah-commanded-muhammad-to-marry-zaynab" data-heading="the-3rd-role-of-revelation-verse-33-38-declares-that-allah-commanded-muhammad-to-marry-zaynab" class="index-link">The 3rd Role of Revelation: Verse 33:38 declares that Allah commanded Muhammad to marry Zaynab</a><li class="index-item"><a href="/03/index.php/en/divine-revelation-or-a-human-drama?format=feed&type=rss#the-4th-role-of-revelation-the-wedding-took-place-directly-in-the-heavens" data-heading="the-4th-role-of-revelation-the-wedding-took-place-directly-in-the-heavens" class="index-link">The 4th Role of Revelation: The wedding took place directly in the heavens </a><li class="index-item"><a href="/03/index.php/en/divine-revelation-or-a-human-drama?format=feed&