<p>Any distant male Relative like <br>Cousin (or even his descendants)</p>
</div>
</td>
<td style="width: 22.2746%; height: 64px; background-color: #bfedd2; border: 1px solid #000000;">
<div>2/3</div>
</td>
<td style="width: 27.2245%; height: 64px; background-color: #fbeeb8; border: 1px solid #000000;">
<div>66.67%</div>
</td>
