			<title>Saf ibn Sayyad (An Equally Important Incident as the Satanic Verses)</title>
			<link>https://sachaai.com/03/index.php/en/divine-revelation-or-a-human-drama/19-saf-ibn-sayyad-an-equally-important-incident-as-the-satanic-verses</link>
